</UL>
<H3>Collections of Internet Links to Environmental Resources</H3>
<UL>

<LI><A HREF="http://www.cnie.org/nle/crs_main.html">CRS Reports</A> - Links to environmental reports issued by the Congressional Research Service


<LI><A HREF="http://www.econet.apc.org/econet/">EcoNet Home Page</A>
<LI><A HREF="http://drseuss.lib.uidaho.edu:70/docs/egj.html">Electronic Green Journal</A>-Information concerning sources on international environmental topics
<LI><A HREF="http://www.clay.net/~jnc/">Environmental Professional's Homepage</A> - <i>clay.net</i>
<LI><A HREF="http://galaxy.einet.net/galaxy/Law/Environmental.html">Environmental (Law)</A> - EINet
<LI><A HREF="http://www.law.indiana.edu/law/intenvlaw.html">Environmental
Law</A> - Indiana Law School </LI>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.law.indiana.edu/envdec/envdec.html">Environmental
Decisionmaking - Appendices</A> </LI>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.igc.apc.org/envlaw/">Environmental Law Around the World @igc</A>
<LI><A HREF="http://envinfo.com/">Environmental Law Information Resources</A> - Morgan, Lewis & Bockius
<LI><A HREF="http://www.pls.com:8001/his/101.htm">Internet Law Library: Environmental, Natural Resource, and Energy Law</A> - House of Representatives
<LI><A HREF="http://www.webdirectory.com/">Environmental organization web directory</A> - "Earth's biggest environment search engine"

<LI><A HREF="http://www.greenpeace.org/~intlaw/index.html">Multilateral Environmental Treaties</A> - Greenpeace
<LI><A HREF="http://www.cnie.org/nle/index.shtml">National library for the environment</A> - A nonprofit organization site with links to CRS reports and a comprehensive "Environmental Encyclopedia" (still in progress)
<LI><A HREF="http://joshua.law.pace.edu/env/environ.html">Pace Global Environmental Law Network</A>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.nrdc.org/nrdc/field/state.html">State of Nature</A> - NDRC Web
<LI><A HREF="http://www.yahoo.com/Environment_and_Nature/Law/">Society and Culture:Environment and Nature:Law</A> - Yahoo
<LI><A HREF="http://www.law.indiana.edu/law/intenvlaw.html">The World Wide Web Virtual Library: Law: International & Environmental Law</A> - Indiana University School of Law, Bloomington
</UL>

