<CENTER>

<H1>Public International Law</H1>

</CENTER>

<BR>





<BR>

<H2><A HREF="annual.htm">New England International and Comparative Law Annual</A></H2> - The <i>Annual</i> publishes student written articles
discussing provocative and current issues in the fields of international
and comparative law.  Online publication is planned for January, 1997. 


<BR>

<BR>



<HR NOSHADE>



<A NAME="Treaties"> 
<H2>Treaties and Multilateral Agreements</H2></A>



<H3>Collections</H3>

<UL>



<LI><A HREF="http://www.tufts.edu/fletcher/multilaterals.html">Fletcher School of Law and Diplomacy</A> - Multilaterals Project

