<CENTER><H1>Private International Law</H1></CENTER>


<A NAME="IP">
<H2>International Intellectual Property</H2></A>

<UL>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.law.cornell.edu/treaties/berne/overview.html">Berne Convention for the Protection of Literary and Artistic Works (Paris Text 1971)</A> - Cornell Law School
<LI><A HREF="http://www.tufts.edu/departments/fletcher/multi/texts/BH423.txt">Rome Convention for the Protection of Performers . . .</A> - Fletcher Multilaterals Project

<LI><A HREF="http://www.uspto.gov/web/menu/menu5.html">Key treaties and Patent information</A> - U.S. Patent and Trademark Office links to International Material
<LI><A HREF="http://www.echo.lu/legal/en/labhome.html">EU material on copyright and data protection</A> - Legal Advisory Board 
<LI><A HREF="http://www.echo.lu/legal/en/ipr/ipr.html">EU directives on copyright</A> - includes Television without Frontiers, software
</UL>

<A NAME="trade">
<H2>International Trade Information Sites</H2></A>

<H3>U.S. Government Sites</H3>
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.usitc.gov/">United States International Trade Commission</A>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.ita.doc.gov/">International Trade Administration</A> - ITA and world trade initiatives
 
<LI><A HREF="http://www.ita.doc.gov/tradebase/">Tradebase</A> -  U.S.<BR>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.ustr.gov/index.html">U.S. Trade Representatives Home Page</A>
</UL>
<H3>Other Trade Sites</H3>

<UL>
<LI><A HREF="http://cisgw3.law.pace.edu/">International Trade database</A> - Pace University's Institute of International Commercial Law - focusing on the United Nations Convention on Contracts for the International Sale of Goods

<LI><A HREF="http://www.ita.doc.gov/ftaa2005/">Free Trade Area of the Americas</A> - iniative to create a Western Hemisphere Free Trade Area by 2005

<LI><A HREF="http://www.wto.org/">World Trade Organization</A> - WTO Home Page<BR>

<LI><A HREF="http://ciber.bus.msu.edu/busres.htm">International Business Resources on the WWW</A> - Michigan State University Center for International Business Education and Research (CIBER)
-- An excellent source

<LI><A HREF="http://www.customs.com/links.html">International Trade Links</A> - Customs links
</LI>
<LI><A HREF="http://www2.echo.lu/echo/en/menuecho.html">European Commission Host Organisation</A> - information services in business - access to 20 online databases

<LI><A HREF="http://ra.irv.uit.no/trade_law/itl.html">International Trade Law Project</A> - ITLP

<LI><A HREF="http://www.tpusa.com/">Trade Point USA</A> - Private site for trade information<BR>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.uk.shops:8000/thedoor.html">The European Directory</A>  - The Doorway into Europe<BR>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.islandnet.com/~wwlia/wwlia.htm">World Wide Legal Information Association
<LI><A HREF="http://www.francecontacts.com/">France World Contacts</A>

</UL>



<A NAME="tradenews">
