          any other supplemental case(s), problem sets or
assignments given

    <LI><I> Foci:</I> <BR>    understanding how federalism works to trump state
          law;
          determining when there should be federal preemptive
          substantive law; determining what should be the shape
          of Apreemptive@ federal common law;
          comparison to Aeerie@ Erie situations where federal law
          is also required, but only in federal courts

   <LI> <I> Supplemental Readings</I>:<BR> You might find helpful for this
     assignment:
         <UL>
