<LI><A HREF="gopher://gopher.undp.org:70/00/undocs/scd/scouncil/s93/28">U.N. Resolution  827 establishing the ICTY</A>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.lib.uchicago.edu/LibInfo/Law/intl.html#warcrimes">War Crimes </A>- U. Chicago
<LI><A HREF="http://www.umn.edu/humanrts/instree/auox.htm">War Crimes and Crimes against Humanity, Including Genocide </A>- U. Minnesota
