<html>

<head>
<title>New England Law Review: Janet Reno Speech</title>
<meta name="GENERATOR" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
</head>

<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" text="#000000" link="#0000FF" vlink="#551A8B" alink="#FF0000">
<!--     DARBY PRINTING COMPANY DTP MACRO STATUS VERSION 2.19 - 02/27/95 - SWO

