http://www.kable.co.uk:80/news/nb20.12pubspend.htm 194.112.40.47 19970105183035 text/html 4668
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sun, 05 Jan 1997 18:30:34 GMT
Server: Apache/1.0.5
