<DOCHDR>
http://www.kable.co.uk:80/sitewatch/fr.index.8.11.htm 194.112.40.47 19970105184117 text/html 7858
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sun, 05 Jan 1997 18:41:14 GMT
Server: Apache/1.0.5
