<head>
<title>Who We Are</title>
<meta name="GENERATOR" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
</head>

<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" link="#808000" vlink="#800080" alink="#00FF00">
<p><img src="images/who.gif" alt="Who we are" align=bottom width=267 height=68>&#160;</p>
<h3><img src="images/people.gif" alt="People" align=absmiddle width=85 height=150></h3>
<p>Founded in 1962, EDS is a world leader in the application of information technology to government and business in 42 
countries around the world. </p>
<p>We employ over 95,000 people world-wide and over 9,000 in the UK alone.</p>
<p>1995 annual turnover exceeded $12 billion, up over 24% on the previous year. Net income was $938.9 million, a rise of 
over 14% on 1994.</p>
<p>The size and scope of EDS goes a very short way to describing who we are. To understand us, you have to examine our 
accomplishments across a wide range of government and commercial sectors. </p>
<p>The Success Stories section featured at the end of each government sector will demonstrate in detail the high level of 
customer satisfaction that has led to a contract renewal rate exceeding 80%.</p>
<hr>
