<html>

<head>
<title>How We Do It</title>
<meta name="GENERATOR" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
</head>

<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" link="#808000" vlink="#800080" alink="#00FF00">
<p><img src="images/how.gif" alt="How We Do It" align=bottom width=290 height=68></p>
<h3><img src="images/people.gif" alt="People" align=absmiddle width=85 height=150></h3>
<p><strong>By Adding Value</strong></p>
<p>We add measurable value to your organisation by thinking creatively and inventively, yet pragmatically.</p>
<p><strong>Closing Gaps</strong></p>
<p>We have become the world&#146;s largest information services supplier by closing the gap between what is theoretically 
possible to achieve using IT and what is actually being achieved in practice.</p>
<p><strong>Specialist Knowledge</strong></p>
<p>This requires two types of expertise:</p>
<ol>
<li>Expertise in the latest technologies. That&#146;s why we are at the forefront of such developing fields as neural networks, 
virtual reality, scanning and image processing, The Internet and intranets. We have set up Centres of Expertise and 
Centres of Excellence in a variety of key technologies areas to maintain leadership in their practical application<br>
</li>
<li>Expertise in particular government sectors. Many EDS employees have been recruited for their knowledge of 
particular fields within government and industry. These are our sector specialists. Furthermore, we are organised in 
groups around these sector specialities, so that we are best positioned to understand and support our customers.</li>
</ol>
<p><strong>Long-term Partnerships</strong></p>
<p>The success of our work depends on the quality of our relationships with our customers. That&#146;s why long-term partnerships 
usually provide the greatest benefit to both parties. These relationships frequently take the form of Outsourcing or 
Co-Sourcing agreements.</p>
<p><strong>Outsourcing</strong></p>
<p>Outsourcing involves taking over the management of an entire system of process and providing our customers with a 
guaranteed level of service.</p>
<p><strong>Co-Sourcing</strong></p>
<p>Co-Sourcing takes this concept one step further. We put our money where our mouth is. With Co-Sourcing, we share our 
clients&#146; risks as well as the rewards generated by the success of our work. </p>
<p><strong>Open-mindedness</strong></p>
<p>Naturally, we&#146;re happy to work on a simple project-by-project basis, where appropriate. But more importantly, we&#146;re 
always open to innovative ways of doing business... and even pioneering uncharted territory. </p>
<p><strong>And Without Boundaries</strong></p>
<p>At EDS, we do not recognise the conventional boundaries of size, place, time or type of project. So whatever goals you 
have in mind, we have the resources not only to meet your needs, but to exceed your expectations. </p>
<hr>
