<BLOCKQUOTE>

<H3>Kable presents the first Signposts to Government competition</H3>
<TABLE WIDTH=75% HEIGHT=25%>
<TR ALIGN=CENTER>
<TD><FONT COLOR=#FF0000>Open to everyone!</BR>
Free and easy to enter!</BR>
Win a fabulous prize!</FONT></BR>
