<html>

<head>
<title>Our View of the Central Government Scene</title>
<meta name="GENERATOR" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
</head>

<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" link="#808000" vlink="#800080" alink="#00FF00">
<p align=left><a href="central.htm"><img src="images/cgovt.gif" alt="Central Government" align=bottom border=0 width=458 height=68></a></p>
<h3 align=left>&#160;<img src="images/bigben1.gif" alt="Big Ben" align=absmiddle width=150 height=288>OUR VIEW OF THE SCENE</h3>
<p align=left>The environment for the provision of public services presents significant challenges for public authorities, agencies, departments and suppliers. </p>
<p align=left>Demand for service continues to rise while the resources for their provision are under constant pressure.</p>
<p align=left>The need to provide value for money stimulates review of efficiency and effectiveness and moves the focus of attention back to the core activity. </p>
<p align=left>Management responds to these demands in several ways. </p>
<ul>
<li><p align=left>New internal markets spread awareness of financial discipline through the service delivery chain </p>
</li>
<li><p align=left>Within the autonomy of agency frameworks, new operational structures are developed to enhance customer service and strengthen financial management </p>
</li>
<li><p align=left>The Private Finance Initiative introduces new supplier relationships and contractual regimes. In this environment, organisations require innovative solutions to 
meet their goals</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p align=left>EDS contributes to this re-shaping process in partnership with central government organisations.<br>
</p>
<hr>
<ul>
<li><font color="#C0C0C0">Our View of the Scene</font></li>
<li><a href="cback.htm"><font size=3>Our Background in Central Government</font></a></li>
<li><a href="cservice.htm"><font size=3>Our Services</font></a></li>
</ul>
<p>&#160;</p>
