<h3><img src="images/mayor1.gif" alt="Mayor" align=absmiddle width=52 height=150><font size=4><strong>EDS SERVICES TO LOCAL GOVERNMENT</strong></font></h3>
<p>EDS services to local government cover the complete lifecycle of a project from identification of the critical issues through to management of your new systems and 
work processes.</p>
<p>The Continuum of Services chart below shows our full lifecycle capabilities.</p>
<p><img src="images/edsdiag.gif" alt="Lifecycle Capabilities Graphic" align=bottom width=400 height=208></p>
