<p>3. System Integration &#150; the integration of computer and communications hardware and software to provide total solutions</p>
<p>4. Systems Management &#150; all aspects of management from planning and provision through operational running to ongoing support of a client&#146;s 
computing environment and communications systems</p>
<p>5. Process Management &#150; undertaking business processes on behalf of the customer organisation to allow the customer to focus on its core 
business objectives&#160;&#160;</p>
</blockquote>
