<html>

<head>
<title>Healthcare services</title>
<meta name="GENERATOR" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
</head>

<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" link="#808000" vlink="#800080" alink="#00FF00">
<p><a href="health.htm"><img src="images/healthtx.gif" alt="Healthcare" align=bottom border=0 width=245 height=66></a></p>
<h3><img src="images/nurse.gif" alt="Nurse" align=absmiddle width=84 height=150>OUR SERVICES</h3>
<p>EDS services to healthcare providers cover the complete lifecycle of a project from identification of the critical issues 
through to management of your systems and work processes.</p>
<p>The Continuum of Services chart below shows our full lifecycle capabilities.</p>
<p><img src="images/edsdiag.gif" alt="Lifecycle Capabilities Graphic" align=bottom width=400 height=208></p>
<p>To describe these services in more detail, we can break them down into five main areas:</p>
<ol>
<li>Consulting - providing strategic business and technical advice to clients</li>
<li>Systems Development - both application and infrastructure software development</li>
<li>System Integration - the integration of computer and communications hardware and software to provide total solutions</li>
<li>Systems Management - all aspects of management from planning and provision through operational running to ongoing 
support of a client&#146;s computing environment and communications systems</li>
<li>Process Management - undertaking business processes on behalf of the customer organisation to allow the customer to 
focus on its core business objectives</li>
</ol>
<p>In addition to these services, we offer an outstanding range of tried and tested healthcare software packages that foster 
efficient management of such areas as:</p>
<ul>
<li>patient administration</li>
<li>waiting lists</li>
<li>in-patient departments</li>
<li>out-patient services</li>
<li>accident and emergency</li>
<li>maternity</li>
<li>case notes tracking</li>
<li>integrated care system</li>
<li>multi-disciplinary planning</li>
<li>medical data indexing and auditing</li>
<li>integrated pathology system</li>
<li>operating theatres management</li>
<li>pharmacy functions</li>
<li>and many other management systems</li>
</ul>
<p>The prime focus of our healthcare strategy in Europe is the effective application of Information and Communication 
Technology (ICT) systems and services. By improving the internal efficiency of healthcare providers through the automation 
of medical care services, EDS aims to improve external efficiency with a flow of integrated information to second services, 
such as insurers and pharmaceutical suppliers.</p>
<hr>
