<head>
<title>London borough of Brent - Business Rates</title>
<meta name="GENERATOR" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
</head>

<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" link="#808000" vlink="#800080" alink="#00FF00">
<p><a href="local.htm"><img src="images/lgovt.gif" alt="Local Government" align=bottom border=0 width=415 height=66></a></p>
<h3><img src="images/mayor1.gif" alt="Mayor" align=absmiddle width=52 height=150><font size=4><strong>LONDON BOROUGH OF BRENT </strong></font></h3>
<p><strong>NATIONAL NON DOMESTIC RATES SERVICE</strong></p>
<p>EDS&#146; partnership with the London Borough of Brent was further consolidated by the award of a seven year contract to administer the National Non Domestic 
Rates Service. </p>
<p>By selecting EDS, the Council has provided its Business Ratepayers with a number of key benefits:</p>
<ul>
<li>Quantifiable improvement in service levels and performance</li>
<li>Reliable, courteous service</li>
<li>Value for money</li>
<li>Effectiveness and efficiency of service</li>
<li>Recognised internal and external accreditation</li>
<li>Strong customer care and easily accessible services</li>
</ul>
<p>By using existing ICL B-Rates software, we have maintained continuity of service to the Ratepayers of Brent. This continuity is further enhanced by employing staff 
with a working knowledge of the locality. Altogether, the staff have over 200 years' experience of working within a rating environment. In addition, EDS has a 
number of professionally qualified IRRV and IPFA staff.</p>
<p>We are now implementing a policy of resolving the queries of Business Ratepayers at first contact. We are accomplishing this aim by having specialist Business Rate 
experts on site. They are assisted by the latest imaging and workflow technology. This gives them instant access to all of the data they need to respond to questions 
quickly and authoritatively. </p>
<p>The control of Brent&#146;s National Non Domestic Rates Service extends EDS&#146; relationship with Brent, which began with their Revenue and Benefit Service business. </p>
