<html>

<head>
<title>Avalon Somerset Health Trust</title>
<meta name="GENERATOR" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
</head>

<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" link="#808000" vlink="#800080" alink="#00FF00">
<p><a href="health.htm"><img src="images/healthtx.gif" alt="Healthcare" align=bottom border=0 width=245 height=66></a></p>
<h3><img src="images/nurse.gif" alt="Nurse" align=absmiddle width=84 height=150>AVALON SOMERSET NHS TRUST</h3>
<p><strong>EDS TO SUPPLY INTEGRATED INFORMATION SYSTEM</strong></p>
<p>EDS will be supplying Avalon Somerset NHS Trust with an integrated clinical information system. Avalon is a learning disabilities trust based in Bridgwater, 
Somerset. It provides care in both acute and community settings by multi-disciplinary teams. </p>
<p>The system comprises two of our own specialised healthcare software packages, SWiftPLAN and SWiftCare. SWiftPLAN is a multi-purpose, multi-disciplinary 
planning tool designed to help key workers and care managers plan care more effectively, allowing providers to demonstrate clearly to purchasers how much 
particular care has cost and why. SWiftCare is a person-based second generation integrate community care system. Its flexible design caters for the differing 
information needs of care professionals and managers, and facilitates efficient recording and monitoring of multi-disciplinary care.</p>
<p>The delivery of these solutions will enable the Trust to improve data quality, consistency and input time by allowing it to standardise the care programme approach 
and avoid clerical input of diary sheets.</p>
<hr>
