<DOCOLDNO>IA015-000163-B036-403</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.kable.co.uk:80/eds/lisa.htm 194.112.40.47 19970105185547 text/html 8190
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Sun, 05 Jan 1997 18:55:43 GMT
Server: Apache/1.0.5
