<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Welcome to AAA</TITLE></HEAD><BODY LINK="#0000bf" VLINK="#ee0000" BGCOLOR="#ffffff" BACKGROUND="aaatile.gif"><center><table cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0><TR><TD><a href="welcome.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="prev.gif" alt="PREV"></a></TD><TD><a href="welcome.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="home.gif" alt="HOME"></a></TD><TD><a href="index.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="navigate.gif" alt="Navigate"></a></TD><TD><a href="aaaautotravel.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="next.gif" alt="NEXT"></a></TD></TR>
</table><h1>Welcome to AAA</h1></center>
<P><!-- This page created by SiteScript a proprietary tool of America Online Productions Inc.
Unauthorized use of this product outside of AOL is a violation of Copyright laws. -->
<img align="right" width=216 height=174 src="histdaringmen.gif"><FONT SIZE=+2><b>W</b></FONT>elcome to the AAA
web page! Since our founding in 1902, the American
Automobile Association has grown from a handful of motoring clubs to become the
world's largest travel and automotive services provider. There are 111 AAA/CAA
clubs with more than 1,000 offices throughout the United States and Canada, and
now we've added a new "virtual" office here on the web.<br clear=all>

<img align="left" width=216 height=174 src="histaaatruck.gif">We're excited about our latest technological
venture, and we think you will be,
too. You'll find our web site loaded with the information you want about
<a href="aaamembershipbenefits.html">AAA Membership Benefits</a>, on the
road and in your hometown. We've got details on
<a href="aaaautotravel.html">Auto Travel</a> and
<a href="aaaautomotiveservices.html">Automotive Services</a>, member savings
through our <a href="aaatravelagencies.html">Travel Agencies</a>
partnerships and <a HREF="showyourcardampsavereg.html">Show Your Card &
Save(R)</A> programs, listings of our U.S. and
Canadian <a href="aaaoffices.html">Offices</a>, links to other
<a href="aaacoolwebsites.html">Cool Web Sites</a> and much more.<br
clear=all>

<img align="right" width=216 height=174 src="histcowtow.gif">And this is only the beginning. As we continue our
journey on the information
highway, we'll be adding new features and benefits on everything from travel to
automotive information to additional savings through AAA.<br clear=all>

So take a trip through the AAA web, and Travel With Someone You Trust(SM).





<P>

