<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>AAA Membership Benefits</TITLE></HEAD><BODY LINK="#0000bf" VLINK="#ee0000" BACKGROUND="aaatile.gif"><center><table cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0><TR><TD><a href="travelbooks.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="prev.gif" alt="PREV"></a></TD><TD><a href="welcome.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="home.gif" alt="HOME"></a></TD><TD><a href="index.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="navigate.gif" alt="Navigate"></a></TD><TD><a href="aaaautomotiveservices.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="next.gif" alt="NEXT"></a></TD></TR>
</table><h1>AAA Membership Benefits</h1></center><img align="right" border=0 width=92 height=83 src="aaamembershipbenefits.gif" alt="AAA Membership Benefits"><!-- This page created by SiteScript a proprietary tool of America Online Productions Inc.
Unauthorized use of this product outside of AOL is a violation of Copyright laws. -->
<FONT SIZE="+2"><B>Y</B></FONT>our AAA membership offers the greatest benefit a
motorist could want: peace of
mind that, no matter where you are, AAA is just a phone call away. But there's
so much more to AAA than Emergency Road Service: We provide a full range of
automotive and travel services and also serve as an advocate for North American
motorists and their rights.<p>

<h3>Travel Services</h3>
<ul>
<li>AAA travel publications and maps covering the United States, Canada,
Mexico, the Caribbean and Europe.
<li>Customized Triptik&reg; routings for the United States and Canada.
<li>More than 1,000 accredited, full-service AAA travel agencies throughout the
United States and Canada.
<li>Special travel discounts through our preferred suppliers program.
<li>Show Your Card &amp; Save&reg; discounts.
<li>Fee-free American Express&reg; Travelers Cheques. 
<li>Reciprocal agreements with international motor clubs for travel abroad.
</ul>
<h3>Automotive Services</h3><img align="right" width=288 height=340 src="membenkeys.gif">
<ul>
<li>Primary membership services: mechanical first aid, flat tire service and
battery boosts.
<li>AAA Plus Membership additional benefits: free emergency fuel and extended
towing.
<li>Emergency road service 24 hours a day through SUPERNUMBER&reg;,
1-800-AAA-HELP.
<li>Emergency Check Acceptance program (up to $250) for emergency repairs.
<li>Repair facility screening through our Approved Auto Repair program.
<li>AAA Mobile Diagnostic Van program (fuel economy and engine performance
testing).
<li>AAA Autograph&reg; new car buying guide.
<li>AutoEase&reg; pricing, buying, leasing and financing service and Vehicle
Finance programs (at participating clubs).
</ul>
<h3>Additional Benefits and Services</h3>
<ul>
<li>AAA/VISA&reg; and AAA/Mastercard&reg; cards.
<li>Club magazine or other publications.
<li>Pamphlets and booklets on traffic safety, driving costs, car care and
buying a car.
<li>Traffic safety programs on driver education and improvement, driver
instructor training, school safety patrols, pedestrian safety, and
drinking-and-driving awareness.
<li>Legislative programs protecting motorists' rights and responsibilities and
the public's interest regarding the infrastructure, travel and tourism, and
environmental policies.
</ul>

For additional information, or to join AAA, please contact your local
<a href="aaaoffices.html">AAA/CAA club office</a>.<p>


 

