<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>AAA Auto Services</TITLE></HEAD><BODY LINK="#0000bf" VLINK="#ee0000" BACKGROUND="aaatile.gif"><center><table cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0><TR><TD><a href="aaamembershipbenefits.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="prev.gif" alt="PREV"></a></TD><TD><a href="welcome.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="home.gif" alt="HOME"></a></TD><TD><a href="index.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="navigate.gif" alt="Navigate"></a></TD><TD><a href="approvedautorepair.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="next.gif" alt="NEXT"></a></TD></TR>
</table><h1>AAA Auto Services</h1></center><img align="right" border=0 width=91 height=84 src="aaaautomotiveservices.gif" alt="AAA Auto Services">AAA is always there for our members, whether you're on the road, buying a car, teaching a teen to drive, or looking for ways to improve your own driving skills. AAA/CAA clubs offer brochures and pamphlets filled with useful information on car care, auto repair, driver safety and other important topics. Local clubs also sponsor safety programs for children, adults, drivers, pedestrians and others.<p>

Of course, one of the most valuable benefits of a AAA membership is our nationwide <a href="emergencyroadservice.html">Emergency Road Service</a> system-- SUPERNUMBER(R)--which guarantees that AAA/CAA members will never be stranded, even if you're a hundred miles from home. And the <a href="approvedautorepair.html">Approved Auto Repair</a> program ensures that members who patronize participating auto repair facilities are receiving the highest quality service available--guaranteed by AAA.<p>

<img align="left" width=144 height=96 src="membensupercard.gif">Just call your <a href="aaaoffices.html">local club</a> to discover all the automotive benefits offered through your AAA membership. You also can learn more about AAA services by visiting our "electronic office" at AAA Online, available to all <a href="http://www.aol.com">America Online</a> subscribers.<p><br clear=all><p>
<hr>

