<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Approved Auto Repair</TITLE></HEAD><BODY LINK="#0000bf" VLINK="#ee0000" BGCOLOR="#ffffff" BACKGROUND="aaatile.gif"><center><table cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0><TR><TD><a href="aaaautomotiveservices.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="prev.gif" alt="PREV"></a></TD><TD><a href="welcome.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="home.gif" alt="HOME"></a></TD><TD><a href="index.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="navigate.gif" alt="Navigate"></a></TD><TD><a href="emergencyroadservice.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="next.gif" alt="NEXT"></a></TD></TR>
</table><h1>Approved Auto Repair</h1></center>
<FORM ACTION="aaa.repair.fcgi" METHOD="POST" >
<INPUT TYPE="hidden" NAME="_COMMAND_" VALUE="GETLIST">
<INPUT TYPE="hidden" NAME="_DATABASE_" VALUE="AAA Repairs.FM">
<INPUT TYPE="hidden" NAME="_RETURN_" VALUE="Return Field">
<FONT SIZE="+2"><B>U</B></FONT>ntimely breakdowns don't always occur on your vacation or far from home--sometimes
they happen in your driveway, at the office, or on the way to the store.
And sometimes, unfortunately, the problem is more than a flat tire or dead
battery. So when you find yourself in need of auto repairs, look for the
"AAA Approved" sign, given only to participants in AAA's Approved
Auto Repair program.<BR>
<BR>
<img align="right" width=91 height=84 src="aaaautomotiveservices.gif">Covering more than 4,000 facilities, this valuable benefit offers members
peace of mind in selecting a repair shop. Approval is based on stringent
criteria regarding technician training and certification, availability of
up-to-date equipment, and proven success in providing customer satisfaction.
And all approved facilities are required to guarantee their work and to
abide by AAA's decision if disputes arise and mediation is necessary.<BR>
<BR>
AAA's Approved Auto Repair program: guaranteeing the highest quality service
for our members.<BR>
<BR>
 For listings and information on local Approved Auto Repair Facilities (in participating areas), please complete the search form shown below.
<BR>
