<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Show Your Card &amp; Save&reg;</TITLE></HEAD><BODY LINK="#0000bf" VLINK="#ee0000" BACKGROUND="aaatile.gif"><center><table cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0><TR><TD><a href="worldexplorercruises.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="prev.gif" alt="PREV"></a></TD><TD><a href="welcome.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="home.gif" alt="HOME"></a></TD><TD><a href="index.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="navigate.gif" alt="Navigate"></a></TD><TD><a href="aaaoffices.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="next.gif" alt="NEXT"></a></TD></TR>
</table><h1>Show Your Card &amp; Save&reg;</h1></center><img align="right" border=0 width=100 height=84 src="showyourcardampsavereg.gif" alt="Show Your Card &amp; Save&reg;">Thousands of lodgings, attractions, restaurants and retail locations throughout the United States and Canada take part in AAA's national Show Your Card &amp; Save(R) program. These exclusive partnerships guarantee AAA members significant benefits and savings--and it's as easy as presenting your membership card. Just look for the Show Your Card & Save sign at participating locations, show a valid AAA membership card and enjoy the savings of your AAA membership.<p>
<center><TABLE BORDER WIDTH=95% ALIGN=center CELLPADDING=6 CELLSPACING=6>
<TH ALIGN=CENTER VLIGH=MIDDLE width=100% colspan=2 ><strong>Accommodations</strong></TH>
<TR><TD ALIGN=CENTER width=20%><img align="middle" width=120 height=106 src="accomclarion.gif" alt="Clarion"></TD><TD><b>Clarion Hotels & Resorts</b><br>AAA members save a minimum 20% discount off rack rates at all Clarion Hotels & Resorts. Just call your local AAA travel office or Choice Hotels' exclusive AAA members-only line, 1-800-228-1222, and have your membership card handy.</TD></TR>
<TR><TD ALIGN=CENTER width=20%><img align="middle" width=120 height=106 src="accomcomfort.gif" alt="Comfort"></TD><TD><b>Comfort Inns</b><br>AAA members save a minimum 10% discount off rack rates at all Comfort Inns. Just call your local AAA travel office or Choice Hotels' exclusive AAA members-only line, 1-800-228-1222, and have your membership card handy.</TD></TR>
<TR><TD ALIGN=CENTER width=20%><img align="middle" width=176 height=90 src="accomdaysinn.gif" alt="Days Inn"></TD><TD><b>Days Inn</b><br>AAA members receive the lowest rates available--from $39--when booked in advance via the AAA toll-free line or through AAA. Just call your local AAA travel office or Days Inns' toll-free AAA line, 1-800-432-9755, and have your membership card handy.</TD></TR>
<TR><TD ALIGN=CENTER width=20%><img align="middle" width=178 height=105 src="accomeconolodge.gif" alt="Econo Lodge"></TD><TD><b>Econo Lodge</b><br>AAA members save a minimum 10% discount off rack rates at all Econo Lodges. Just call your local AAA travel office or Choice Hotels' exclusive AAA members-only line, 1-800-228-1222, and have your membership card handy.
