of greater discounts on admission tickets available through the club.</TD></TR><TR><TD ALIGN=CENTER width=20%><img align="middle" width=120 height=106 src="universalstudios.gif" alt="universalstudios"></TD><TD><b>Universal Studios</b><br>AAA members save $3 on admission at the gate and 10% on souvenirs and selected dining by showing a membership card. Check with your local AAA travel office for the availability of greater discounts on admission tickets at the club.</TD></TR>
