</table><h1>Alaska Sightseeing/Cruise West</h1></center>
<H3>Members Only Vacation Values:</H3>

<img align="right" width=295 height=120 src="alaskasight.gif" alt="Alaska SIghtseeing">Take advantage of the exciting travel opportunities and discounts that come with your AAA membership.<p>

On an Alaska Sightseeing/Cruise West vacation, you can go where the big ships can't. And, as a AAA member, you can save where non-members can't.<p>

<UL>
<LI>AAA members save $50 per person on 4-, 5-, 7- and 10-night Alaska Cruises and Cruise/Tours.
<LI>Save $50 per person off 7-night, 1,000-mile Columbia & Snake River Cruises, round trip from Portland.
<LI>Save $50 per person off 7-night Canada-Inside Passage and Puget Sound Cruises.
<LI>Save $25 per person off 3- & 4-night California Wine Country Cruises, round trip from San Francisco.
<LI>Save $25 per person off 3- & 4-night Glacier Bay Cruises.
</UL>

<H3>About Alaska Sightseeing/Cruise West:</H3>

<img align="left" width=289 height=190 src="alaskaship.gif" alt="Alaska SIghtseeing">Alaska Sightseeing/Cruise West is an American-owned, family-operated company, serving travelers for over 40 years.<p>

Alaska Sightseeing/Cruise West is a small ship cruising experience with cruises and cruise/tours in Alaska, cruises on the Columbia and Snake Rivers, up Canada's Inside Passage, and a California Wine Country Cruise.<p>
<br clear=all>
<p>Alaska Sightseeing/Cruise West offers two styles of yacht touring:<p>

<OL TYPE=1 START="1">
<LI>Daylight Yacht Tours -- in which you cruise only during daylight hours and sleep ashore at night, and

<LI>Overnight Cruising -- where you cruise into the evening and enjoy the on-board comforts of your vessel.
</OL>
<p>
For additional information on this special travel value, contact your local <a href="aaaoffices.html">AAA/CAA club office</a>.<p>

