<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Brennan Tours</TITLE></HEAD><BODY LINK="#0000bf" VLINK="#ee0000" BGCOLOR="#ffffff" BACKGROUND="aaatile.gif"><center><table cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0><TR><TD><a href="thebigredboat.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="prev.gif" alt="PREV"></a></TD><TD><a href="welcome.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="home.gif" alt="HOME"></a></TD><TD><a href="index.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="navigate.gif" alt="Navigate"></a></TD><TD><a href="carnivalcruiselines.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="next.gif" alt="NEXT"></a></TD></TR>
</table><h1>Brennan Tours</h1></center>
<H3>Members Only Vacation Values:</H3>
<img align="right" width=298 height=198 src="brennanphoto1.gif" alt="brennanphoto1.gif">
Take advantage of the exciting travel opportunities and discounts that come with your AAA membership.<p>

Brennan Tours specializes in itineraries which highlight the natural history and scenery of its destinations, such as the Canadian and U.S. Rockies, The Maritimes, New England, the Grand Canyon, Copper Canyon in Mexico, and the U.S. national parks. These destinations, dominated by scenic mountains, waterfalls, canyons, and magnificent coastal seascapes, create memories that can last a lifetime.<p>

Your AAA membership entitles you to a $50 per couple ($25 per person) discount when you book the Brennan Tour of your choice at your local AAA Travel Agency.<p>

<H3>About Brennan Tours:</H3>
<img align="left" width=200 height=300 src="brennanphoto2.gif" alt="brennanphoto2.gif">

Beginning 18 years ago as a specialist in escorted motorcoach tours to the Canadian Rockies, Brennan Tours today operates thirteen escorted tour itineraries in Canada, the United States and Mexico.<p>

Typical features of all Brennan programs include:
<UL>
<LI>Well-located hotels
<LI>A-la-carte Dining
<LI>Enthusiastic, experienced Tour Directors and Drivers
<LI>Personalized service
<LI>Pre-Tour hotel night in the departure city on every tour
</UL>

By focusing on a limited number of itineraries, Brennan is able to pay careful attention to feedback from clients and escorts, and respond in a way that keeps loyal clientele returning to travel again with Brennan Tours.<p>

For additional information on this special travel value, contact your local <a href="aaaoffices.html">AAA/CAA club office</a>.<p>
<br clear=all>

