<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Carnival Cruise Lines</TITLE></HEAD><BODY LINK="#0000bf" VLINK="#ee0000" BGCOLOR="#ffffff" BACKGROUND="aaatile.gif"><center><table cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0><TR><TD><a href="brennantours.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="prev.gif" alt="PREV"></a></TD><TD><a href="welcome.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="home.gif" alt="HOME"></a></TD><TD><a href="index.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="navigate.gif" alt="Navigate"></a></TD><TD><a href="certifiedvacations.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="next.gif" alt="NEXT"></a></TD></TR>
</table><h1>Carnival Cruise Lines</h1></center>
<H3>Members Only Vacation Values:</H3>
<img align="right" width=206 height=183 src="carnivallogo.gif" alt="carnivallogo.gif">
Take advantage of the exciting vacation opportunities and savings that come with your AAA membership.<p>

When you book your Carnival cruise vacation through a AAA Travel Agency, you can take advantage of these special member benefits:<p>

<UL>
<LI>Enjoy special savings on 200 selected departures on the "Fun Ships" of Carnival Cruise Lines.  Save $30 per cabin on a 3- or 4- day cruise; save $50 per cabin on a 7-day cruise.
<LI>On all Carnival cruise vacations, you may take advantage of Air/Sea packages which offer free airfare from most U.S. cities, including transportation to/from the airport.
<LI>Watch for cruise sales throughout the year at your local AAA Travel Agency to enjoy upgrades on selected sailings and other special limited time offers for AAA members only.
<LI>And, ask your AAA travel agent about Carnival's Super Saver discount program.
</UL>

Some restrictions apply.  Additional savings for selected sailings are on a per cabin basis.  Savings noted are in addition to the Super Saver discounts at the time of booking.  Category 4 or better.  Not combinable with other promotions or upgrades.  Capacity controlled.<p>

<H3>About Carnival Cruise Lines:</H3>
<img align="left" width=302 height=200 src="carnivalphoto1.gif" alt="carnivalphoto1.gif">

If your kind of fun means days spent lounging in the sun, nights of thrilling entertainment, exciting tropical ports of call, fine dining, pampering service and an endless variety of activities, then a Carnival cruise is for you.  And all of these features are included for one low price.<p>

On a Carnival cruise, there's never any packing or unpacking as you sail from port to port.  No matter what your age or interests may be, from the moment you step aboard a "Fun Ship," Carnival promises an unforgettable vacation.<p>

For additional information on this special travel value, contact your local <a href="aaaoffices.html">AAA/CAA club office</a>.<p>
<br clear=all>

