<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Certified Vacations</TITLE></HEAD><BODY LINK="#0000bf" VLINK="#ee0000" BGCOLOR="#ffffff" BACKGROUND="aaatile.gif"><center><table cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0><TR><TD><a href="carnivalcruiselines.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="prev.gif" alt="PREV"></a></TD><TD><a href="welcome.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="home.gif" alt="HOME"></a></TD><TD><a href="index.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="navigate.gif" alt="Navigate"></a></TD><TD><a href="classichawaii.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="next.gif" alt="NEXT"></a></TD></TR>
</table><h1>Certified Vacations</h1></center>
<H3>Members Only Vacation Values:</H3>
<img align="left" width=206 height=183 src="certifiedphoto1.gif" alt="certifiedphoto1.gif">
Take advantage of the exciting travel opportunities and discounts that come with your AAA membership.<p>

Certified Vacations can take you to a variety of glorious, sunny spots in the Caribbean and Bermuda, and to terrific destinations in the USA.<p>

When you book a Certified Vacation -- including Caribbean Trends, Cayman Air Tours, Delta Dream Vacations or American Express Florida Vacations -- through your AAA Travel Agency, you receive a complimentary gift photo album for every two fully paid adults!<p>
<br clear=all>
<H3>About Certified Vacations:</H3>
<img align="right" width=200 height=133 src="certifiedphoto2.gif" alt="certifiedphoto2.gif">

With a commitment to customer satisfaction, Certified Vacations are developed in conjunction with the most respected names in the travel industry. Certified Vacations take you to many of the most popular destinations around, from Bermuda and the Bahamas when you are seeking the sun, to Colorado and other Rocky Mountain states when you are looking for the ideal place to snow ski.<p>

Delta Dream Vacations, for example, include round-trip air transportation via Delta Air Lines, hotel and resort accommodations, round-trip airport transfers or rental car, and value-packed bonus features.  Every part of every vacation package is thoroughly inspected to ensure the highest quality.<p>

The new Caribbean Trends program includes vacation packages to Aruba, the Bahamas, Barbados, the Cayman Islands, Jamaica, Puerto Rico and Bermuda.<p>

For additional information on this special travel value, contact your local <a href="aaaoffices.html">AAA/CAA club office</a>.<p>

