<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Classic Hawaii</TITLE></HEAD><BODY LINK="#0000bf" VLINK="#ee0000" BGCOLOR="#ffffff" BACKGROUND="aaatile.gif"><center><table cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0><TR><TD><a href="certifiedvacations.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="prev.gif" alt="PREV"></a></TD><TD><a href="welcome.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="home.gif" alt="HOME"></a></TD><TD><a href="index.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="navigate.gif" alt="Navigate"></a></TD><TD><a href="crystalcruises.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="next.gif" alt="NEXT"></a></TD></TR>
</table><h1>Classic Hawaii</h1></center>
<H3>Members Only Vacation Values:</H3>
<img align="right" width=107 height=178 src="classichawaiivaclogo.gif" alt="classichawaiivaclogo.gif">
Take advantage of the exciting travel opportunities and discounts that come with your AAA membership.<p>

As a AAA member, you can see Hawaii in Classic style and enjoy special value-added benefits.<p>

<UL>
<LI>Classic has selected the more unique and exciting adventures available in the islands and made them available to book in advance.  As a AAA member, you get a special 20% discount off prepaid extra sightseeing -- allowing you not just to visit Hawaii, but to experience the best it has to offer -- at a great savings.
<LI>Value-added offers such as room upgrades, extra hotel nights, cars, special meals and more are available at no extra cost to AAA members.
</UL>
<H3>About Classic Hawaii:</H3>
<img align="left" width=200 height=133 src="classichawvacphoto1.gif" alt="classichawaiivacphoto1.gif">

Classic Hawaii offers vacations tailored to fit your individual travel style and schedule, so you can do what you want in Hawaii.  Classic can arrange your air reservations, accommodations at over 100 resort hotels and condominiums on all  six major islands, a car rental, van or limousine transfer and a variety of special services such as charter fishing, helicopter flights over volcanoes, or a challenging day of golf.<p>

Best of all, even with all Classic's special service enhancements, it costs no more to have Classic Hawaii create your own custom vacation with one phone call from your AAA travel agent rather than calling each airline, hotel and car rental company directly.<p>

Classic offers custom vacations at wholesale prices and guarantees that no component of your vacation will be more expensive than booking the identical component directly with the hotel, airline or car rental company.<p>

For additional information on this special travel value, contact your local <a href="aaaoffices.html">AAA/CAA club office</a>.<p>

