<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Delta Queen Steamboat Co. </TITLE></HEAD><BODY LINK="#0000bf" VLINK="#ee0000" BGCOLOR="#ffffff" BACKGROUND="aaatile.gif"><center><table cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0><TR><TD><a href="crystalcruises.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="prev.gif" alt="PREV"></a></TD><TD><a href="welcome.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="home.gif" alt="HOME"></a></TD><TD><a href="index.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="navigate.gif" alt="Navigate"></a></TD><TD><a href="dertravel.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="next.gif" alt="NEXT"></a></TD></TR>
</table><h1>Delta Queen Steamboat Co. </h1></center>
<H3>Members Only Vacation Values:</H3>
<img align="right" width=176 height=153 src="deltaqueenlogo.gif" alt="deltaqueenlogo.gif">
Take advantage of the exciting travel opportunities and discounts that come with your AAA membership.<p>

As a AAA member, you will receive extra benefits on your Steamboatin' vacation.  Book any vacation of 7 nights or more at least 8 months in advance, and receive Free Round Trip Airfare and a $100 Savings Booklet containing coupons redeemable for on-board savings.  Or book any vacation of 6 nights or less at least 8 months in advance and receive a $150 per person Airfare Allowance plus your $100 Savings Booklet.<p>

Book any vacation at least 6 months in advance, and receive a $50 Savings Booklet.  The earlier you book, the more you save!  There has never been a better time to be a AAA member and to go Steamboatin'!<p>

<H3>About Delta Queen Steamboat Co.:</H3>
<img align="left" width=200 height=133 src="deltaqueenphoto1.gif" alt="deltaqueenphoto1.gif">

Since 1890, the Delta Queen Steamboat Co. has served as the keeper of the great steamboat legacy, offering unforgettable vacations on America's only three authentic steam-powered overnight paddlewheelers, the <I>Delta Queen</I>, <I>Mississippi Queen</I>, and brand new <I>American Queen</I>.<p>

The American flagships of the Delta Queen Steamboat Company offer travelers a magical, nostalgic, romantic celebration of the American spirit on a unique vacation in which they experience a cruise on an elegant, authentic paddlewheeler while enjoying modern comforts and conveniences.  With only 87 to 222 staterooms, these intimate steamboats make one feel like the guest of honor in a fine old home.<p>

Vacations depart from more than 12 port cities on nine inland waterways throughout the year.  Many Steamboatin' vacations feature a theme of special interest with special on-board entertainment.<p>

For additional information on this special travel value, contact your local <a href="aaaoffices.html">AAA/CAA club office</a>.<p>

