<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>DER Travel</TITLE></HEAD><BODY LINK="#0000bf" VLINK="#ee0000" BGCOLOR="#ffffff" BACKGROUND="aaatile.gif"><center><table cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0><TR><TD><a href="deltaqueensteamboatco.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="prev.gif" alt="PREV"></a></TD><TD><a href="welcome.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="home.gif" alt="HOME"></a></TD><TD><a href="index.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="navigate.gif" alt="Navigate"></a></TD><TD><a href="disneyvacations.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="next.gif" alt="NEXT"></a></TD></TR>
</table><h1>DER Travel</h1></center>
<H3>Members Only Vacation Values:</H3>
<img align="right" width=206 height=183 src="derphoto1.gif" alt="derphoto1.gif">
Take advantage of the exciting travel opportunities and discounts that come with your AAA membership.<p>

As a AAA member, when you book your DER Travel vacation through a AAA Travel Agency, you will receive a specially designed security pouch for carrying your passport, money and travelers checks around your neck, tucked safely under your clothes.  Also includes a pocket calculator and a handy notebook and pen.<p>

<H3>About DER Travel:</H3>
<img align="left" width=132 height=200 src="derphoto2.gif" alt="derphoto2.gif">

DER has been serving travelers in Europe since 1917.  Today, DER Travel Services is a one-stop travel supplier featuring discounted air tickets, European rail, car rental and hotels, and a variety of vacation packages in Europe and Asia.<p>

For additional information on this special travel value, contact your local <a href="aaaoffices.html">AAA/CAA club office</a>.<p>
<br clear=all>

