<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Disney Vacations</TITLE></HEAD><BODY LINK="#0000bf" VLINK="#ee0000" BGCOLOR="#ffffff" BACKGROUND="aaatile.gif"><center><table cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0><TR><TD><a href="dertravel.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="prev.gif" alt="PREV"></a></TD><TD><a href="welcome.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="home.gif" alt="HOME"></a></TD><TD><a href="index.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="navigate.gif" alt="Navigate"></a></TD><TD><a href="generaltours.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="next.gif" alt="NEXT"></a></TD></TR>
</table><h1>Disney Vacations</h1></center>
<H3>AAA Vacations/Walt Disney World Resort:</H3>
<img align="right" width=200 height=300 src="disneyvacdworldbook.gif" alt="disneyvacdworldbook.gif">
Select a AAA Vacations/Walt Disney World Resort package, and take your choice of many varieties of packages featuring over 14 Walt Disney World Resort Hotels.<p>

Your special package can include:  hotel accommodations, unlimited Magic Pass to all Theme Parks, exclusive Early Theme Park Entry, unlimited Walt Disney World Transportation to all areas of the Resort, selected Resort recreational facilities (nominal fee for some), and Resort Guest Services.<p>

You can also select special packages specifically designed for:<p>

<UL>
<LI>Weddings
<LI>Honeymoon Escapes
<LI>Golf Getaways
<LI>Sunshine Getaways in the Winter
<LI>Fall Fantasy in the Autumn
<LI>Jolly Holidays just before Christmas
<LI>Discovery Packages at the Disney Institute
<LI>AAA Disney Driveaway Vacations
</UL>

<H3>AAA Vacations/Disneyland:</H3>
<img align="left" width=200 height=300 src="disneyvacdlandbook.gif" alt="disneyvacdlandbook.gif">

Select a AAA Vacations/Disneyland package, and take your choice of one of the many varieties of packages featuring a number of Disneyland and Anaheim area hotels including The Disneyland Hotel and The Disneyland Pacific Hotel. <p> 

Your special package can include: hotel accommodations, AAA "Free Days" Flex Passport, Magic Morning (early entrance to Disneyland Park - does not operate daily), transportation daily between your hotel/motel and Disneyland Park, "Where Everyone's a Kid Again" Commemorative Certificate, Southern California Fun Book and free parking at Disneyland Park.<p>

<H3>AAA Disney Driveaway Vacations (Walt Disney World):</H3>

AAA and Walt Disney Attractions have developed an exclusive package for AAA members driving to Walt Disney World.  This package features:<p>

<UL>
<LI>3 nights or more at any of the select Walt Disney World Resort hotels
<LI>2 nights accommodations en route at your choice of participating Choice Hotels and La Quinta Inns
<LI>Exclusive Travel Activity Kit - a collection of Disney Merchandise in an attractive Canvas Bag (with special items for each child age 3 - 9!)
<LI>Unlimited Admission throughout your stay to all Disney Theme Parks
<LI>Early Entry into Theme Parks and use of selected attractions one hour before Parks open to the general public  (available on selected days)
<LI>Disney's Flex Feature
<LI>Preferred Parking in AAA Diamond Parking Lots located at the entrance to Magic Kingdom, Epcot and Disney-MGM Studios
<LI>Exclusive personalized routings, the AAA Triptik(R)
<LI>And more ...
</UL>

<H3>AAA Disney Driveaway Vacations (Disneyland):</H3>

AAA and Walt Disney Attractions have developed an exclusive package for AAA members driving to Disneyland/Southern California.  This package features:

<UL>
<LI>2 nights or more at the Disneyland Hotel, The Disneyland Pacific Hotel or select Anaheim Area Hotels
<LI>2 nights accommodations en route at your choice of participating Choice Hotels and La Quinta Inns
<LI>Exclusive Travel Activity Kit - a collection of Disney Merchandise in an attractive Canvas Bag (with special items for each child age 3 - 11!)
<LI>AAA "Free Days" Flex Passport (enjoy 5 consecutive days of unlimited admission to Disneyland Park for the price of 2 days)
<LI>Magic Morning including entrance to Disneyland Park one hour prior to opening to the general public.  (Does not operate daily.)
<LI>"Where Everyone's a Kid Again" Commemorative Certificate
<LI>Free Parking at Disneyland Park in conjunction with a valid AAA "Free Days" Flex Passport
<LI>Exclusive personalized routings, the AAA Triptik(R)
<LI>And more ...
</UL>

Many package plans offer exclusive AAA member benefits.  Contact your nearest <a href="aaaoffices.html">AAA/CAA office</a> for details on these benefits and how to join AAA.<p>

