<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>General Tours</TITLE></HEAD><BODY LINK="#0000bf" VLINK="#ee0000" BGCOLOR="#ffffff" BACKGROUND="aaatile.gif"><center><table cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0><TR><TD><a href="disneyvacations.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="prev.gif" alt="PREV"></a></TD><TD><a href="welcome.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="home.gif" alt="HOME"></a></TD><TD><a href="index.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="navigate.gif" alt="Navigate"></a></TD><TD><a href="globuscosmos.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="next.gif" alt="NEXT"></a></TD></TR>
</table><h1>General Tours</h1></center>
<H3>Members Only Vacation Values:</H3>
<img align="right" width=250 height=167 src="generalphoto2.gif" alt="generalphoto1.gif">
Take advantage of the exciting travel opportunities and discounts that come with your AAA membership.<p>

General Tours has been the largest operator of tours to Russia and Eastern Europe, carrying more than half a million Americans for nearly 5 decades. General Tours also operates tours to India, Nepal, Turkey, Morocco, Israel, Egypt, Syria and Jordan with an uncompromising level of quality, service and attention to detail.<p>

As a AAA member, you will receive a complimentary excursion on the General Tour you book through your AAA Travel Agency. This exclusive member benefit is for a specific excursion chosen by General Tours, unique to each tour, and is valued at $35 - $75 per person.  Other tour members may join, but are required to pay.<p>

The special AAA member benefit for each of the 46 tours offered by General Tours varies.  For example, tours available this winter to Russia -- starting at only $799 including airfare -- will include for AAA members a visit to see Russian art from the 12th century to the present on a visit to the prestigious Russian Museum located in the heart of St. Petersburg.<p>

<H3>About General Tours:</H3>
<img align="left" width=200 height=300 src="generalphoto1.gif" alt="generalphoto2.gif">

With General Tours, you know you're traveling with the experts to Eastern Europe, Russia and Turkey. Their success in taking American travelers to the world's most interesting places is the result of an unwavering commitment to delight their customers.<p>

General Tour's service includes:

<UL>
<LI>Its own staff of Russia-based local customer service managers, representatives and Russian tour managers, known as the "Russian Service Corps." It is the only American company to have such a service.
<LI>Representative offices in Budapest & Prague, and full-time Customer Service Managers in Moscow, St. Petersburg and Budapest to provide an extra level of service to General Tours' travelers.
<LI>The GeneralAssist network which provides professionals available on call 24 hours a day and access to Western-quality health care in Moscow and St. Petersburg.
<LI>Guaranteed departures on most tour packages.
<LI>Modern luxury motorcoaches in Turkey, Russia and Eastern Europe.
<LI>Carefully selected hotels for good location, private baths or showers, and a pleasant atmosphere.
<LI>Comprehensive sightseeing at every stop when listed and, when inside visits are part of the itinerary, entrance fees are included.
<LI>Complete consumer protection of all travel funds paid for your trip.
<LI>And much more.
</UL>
<br clear=all>
For additional information on this special travel value, contact your local <a href="aaaoffices.html">AAA/CAA club office</a>.<p>

