</table><h1>Globus & Cosmos</h1></center>
<H3>Members Only Vacation Values:</H3>
<img align="right" width=146 height=146 src="globuscosmoslogo.gif" alt="globuscosmoslogo.gif">
Take advantage of the exciting travel opportunities and discounts that come with your AAA membership.<p>

When you book your Globus & Cosmos vacation through a AAA Travel Agency, you'll receive a $25 Travel Dollar Certificate for each AAA client on any Globus or Cosmos Australia & New Zealand, Orient, or South  & Central America Tour, which may be applied toward final payment on that tour.<p>

Also, in 1996, there are exclusive AAA departures to Europe, including a free hotel night after the tour in London and a special AAA Cocktail party.<p>

<H3>About Globus & Cosmos:</H3>
<img align="left" width=140 height=139 src="globuscosmosphoto1.gif" alt="globuscosmosphoto1.gif">

Globus & Cosmos offer First Class and Budget escorted touring to Europe and Britain, USA, Hawaii, Mexico, Canada,  Asia, the Orient, South Pacific, Middle East, Africa, India, and South and Central America. In business since 1928, Globus & Cosmos enjoys a high percentage of customers who return to tour year after year.<p>

Globus tours provide travelers with first-class hotels, most meals, most sightseeing and a tour guide.  Travelers are all English speaking, and all age groups are represented.  Globus has a reputation for first-class service at reasonable prices and has served over 3 million travelers.<p>

Bargain Cosmos, with its quality low-cost tours, has served over 1 million  repeat guests on budget vacations all over the world.  Cosmos touring includes tourist-class hotels, most meals in Europe, basic sightseeing (optional excursions available for sale) and a tour guide at prices that are 30% lower than Globus.<p>

For additional information on this special travel value, contact your local <a href="aaaoffices.html">AAA/CAA club office</a>.<p>

