<H3>Members Only Vacation Values:</H3>
<img align="right" width=297 height=140 src="hollalphoto1.gif" alt="hollalphoto1.gif">

Take advantage of the exciting travel opportunities and discounts that come with your AAA membership.<p>

With nearly 50 years of experience in Alaska and the Yukon, Holland America Westours is a leader in both cruises and tours to the great land of Alaska.<p>

And now, available only to AAA members in the USA and Canada, Holland America Line - Westours and AAA are offering an exclusive Cruise-Tour Program including FREE special member benefits valued at over $190 per couple! This fabulous vacation program for AAA members includes three unique itineraries (two for CAA) with over 90 departures.<p>

<UL>
<li>Exclusively for AAA members is the "Hosted Denali Gold Rush Tour," 12 days/11 nights (Tour #96AA03).  For detailed itinerary, see Tour #3 in the Holland America Alaska Tour brochure.  Highlights of this Cruise-Tour include:
<UL>
<LI>Ketchikan Totem Bight
<LI>Westmark Skagway dinner
<LI>McKinley Explorer dinner
<LI>AAA special discount
</UL>
Value:  US $194 per person


<LI>Exclusively for CAA members is the "Denali Gold Rush Hosted Tour," 11 days/ 10 nights. (Tour #96AA82).  For detailed itinerary, see Tour #82 in the Holland America Canadian Alaska Cruises brochure. Highlights of this Cruise-Tour include:
<ul>
<LI>Ketchikan Totem Bight
<LI>Westmark Skagway dinner
<LI>McKinley Explorer dinner
<LI>CAA special discount
</ul>
Value:  Canadian $252 per person

<LI>Exclusively for AAA members, the "Denali Great Land Hosted Tour" is 13 days/12 nights. (Tour #96AA20).  For detailed itinerary, see Tour #20 in the Holland America Alaska Tour brochure. Highlights of this tour include:
<ul>
<LI>McKinley Explorer dinner
<LI>Juneau Mendenhall Glacier
<LI>Ketchikan Totem Bight
<LI>AAA special discount
</ul>
Value:  US $192 per person

<LI>Exclusively for CAA members, the "Denali Great Land Hosted Tour" is 13 days/12 nights. (Tour #96AA88).  For detailed itinerary, see Tour #88 in the Holland America Canadian Alaska Cruises brochure. Highlights of this tour include:
<ul>
<LI>McKinley Explorer dinner
<LI>Juneau Mendenhall Glacier
<LI>Ketchikan Totem Bight
<LI>CAA special discount
</ul>
Value:  Canadian $250 per person

<LI>Exclusively for AAA members, "Deluxe Escorted Canadian Rockies Tour," 16 days/15 nights.  (Tour #96AA39).  For detailed itinerary see Tour #39 in the Holland America Alaska Tour brochure.  Highlights of this tour include:
<ul>
<LI>Ketchikan Totem Bight
<LI>Juneau Mendenhall Glacier
<LI>Sitka Historical Tour
<LI>AAA special discount
</ul>
Value:  $190 per person
</UL>

Also, In 1996, during five 1-week sales at all AAA Travel Agencies, members will receive an exclusive two category upgrade on Holland America Line - Westours! (on selected sailing dates)<p>

<H3>About Holland America Line - Westours:</H3>
<img align="left" width=200 height=200 src="hollalphoto2.gif" alt="hollalphoto2.gif">

Holland America has a tradition of over 120 years of excellence in providing classic, luxury cruises.  Today, her ships mix the style, service and special touches of great ocean liners with state-of-the-art facilities.  Guests have a wide range of options on Holland America Line ships -- destinations in and of themselves -- from casual to elegant, active to leisurely.<p>

Named "Best Cruise Value" three years in a row by Ocean & Cruise News, Holland America offers numerous small touches overlooked by other cruise lines.  Holland America's Filipino and Indonesian staff provide impeccable service and attend to the smallest details to please cruise guests.  Fresh flowers can be found in abundance throughout the ships as can over $1 million worth of art and antiques.<p>

In Alaska, Holland America Westours is the leading travel provider with 43 land tour itineraries including fully escorted and hosted tours, luxury full-domed rail cars, motorcoaches, dayboats and many exclusive optional excursions.<p>
<br clear=all>
For additional information on this special travel value, contact your local <a href="aaaoffices.html">AAA/CAA club office</a>.<p>


