<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Islands in the Sun</TITLE></HEAD><BODY LINK="#0000bf" VLINK="#ee0000" BGCOLOR="#ffffff" BACKGROUND="aaatile.gif"><center><table cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0><TR><TD><a href="hollandamericalinewestour.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="prev.gif" alt="PREV"></a></TD><TD><a href="welcome.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="home.gif" alt="HOME"></a></TD><TD><a href="index.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="navigate.gif" alt="Navigate"></a></TD><TD><a href="pleasantholidays.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="next.gif" alt="NEXT"></a></TD></TR>
</table><h1>Islands in the Sun</h1></center>
<H3>Members Only Vacation Values:</H3>
<img align="right" width=200 height=133 src="islandinsunlogo.gif" alt="islandinsunlogo.gif">

Take advantage of the exciting travel opportunities and discounts that come with your AAA membership.<p>

Explore legendary Tahiti and the South Pacific with AAA member discounts.

<UL>
<LI>$50 per person discount on selected Tahiti packages.
</UL><br clear=all>

<H3>About Islands in the Sun:
</H3>
<img align="left" width=200 height=139 src="islandsphoto2.gif" alt="islandsphoto2.gif">
Islands in the Sun has introduced more people to the pleasures of Tahiti than any other American travel company ... nearly 200,000 travelers during the past 30 years, and is considered the "pioneer" of American tourism to Tahiti.  The people at Islands in the Sun have what can only be described as an ongoing "love affair" with these islands.  Their philosophy is simple: to share with their clients the same magical experience that each had the first time.<p>

In addition to Tahiti and her sister islands, Islands in the Sun offers more of the South Pacific including friendly Fiji and other exotic South Seas island destinations -- the Samoas, Tonga, the Cook Islands, Vanuatu and the Solomon Islands.<p>

For additional information on this special travel value, contact your local <a href="aaaoffices.html">AAA/CAA club office</a>.<p>

