<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Pleasant Holidays</TITLE></HEAD><BODY LINK="#0000bf" VLINK="#ee0000" BGCOLOR="#ffffff" BACKGROUND="aaatile.gif"><center><table cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0><TR><TD><a href="islandsinthesun.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="prev.gif" alt="PREV"></a></TD><TD><a href="welcome.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="home.gif" alt="HOME"></a></TD><TD><a href="index.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="navigate.gif" alt="Navigate"></a></TD><TD><a href="princesscruises.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="next.gif" alt="NEXT"></a></TD></TR>
</table><h1>Pleasant Holidays</h1></center>
<H3>Members Only Vacation Values:</H3>
<img align="right" width=206 height=183 src="pleasantholphoto1.gif" alt="pleasantholphoto1.gif">

Take advantage of the exciting travel opportunities and discounts that come with your AAA membership.<p>

This year, AAA members can pack even more enjoyment into a great Pleasant Holidays Hawaiian vacation -- with a $30 gift certificate.  Book any Pleasant Holidays Hawaiian vacation with 5 or more hotel nights, and each AAA member will receive a $30 gift certificate toward the purchase of optional sightseeing in Hawaii. Just show your AAA membership card when using your gift certificate.<p>

<H3>About Pleasant Holidays:</H3>
<img align="left" width=295 height=132 src="pleasantholphoto2.gif" alt="pleasantholphoto2.gif">

Pleasant Hawaiian Holidays has sent over 3.5 million visitors to Hawaii since 1959 and has, by far, the widest array of vacation package options to the Hawaiian Islands.  Over the years, Pleasant has developed a reputation for giving its customers an unparalleled level of personal attention, with 22 customer service desks throughout the islands and the largest service staff in Hawaii.  Pleasant's large travel volume and decades of experience allow it to offer customers great value vacations and high quality service -- all at very reasonable prices.<p>

Pleasant has made travel to Hawaii easy. Whether you desire economy or luxury, hotel or condominium, standard airfare or First Class, airport transfers of car rental, Pleasant has something for everyone -- even financing for your vacation.  And now, in addition to the spectacular beauty of Hawaii, Pleasant also offers some of the finest hotels and resorts in Mexico through Pleasant Mexico Holidays.<p>

For additional information on this special travel value, contact your local <a href="aaaoffices.html">AAA/CAA club office</a>.<p>

