<H3>Members Only Vacation Values:</H3>
<img align="right" width=271 height=127 src="royalcarphoto1.gif" alt="royalcarphoto1.gif">

Take advantage of the exciting travel opportunities and discounts that come with your AAA membership.<p>

When you book your Royal Caribbean Cruise vacation through a AAA Travel Agency, you can take advantage of these outstanding cruise offers:<p>

<UL>
<LI>Free accommodation upgrade for AAA/CAA members on selected ships and sailing dates.

<LI>During three scheduled "National Cruise Sales," Royal Caribbean Cruises will offer additional value-added bonuses.
</UL>

And on all Royal Caribbean Cruises, round-trip air is included from most gateway cities, all transfers to and from the ship, plus Royal Caribbean's meet-and-assist program.<p>

<H3>About Royal Caribbean Cruise Lines:</H3>
<img align="left" width=134 height=200 src="royalcarphoto2.gif" alt="royalcarphoto2.gif">

One of the world's largest cruise lines, Royal Caribbean Cruises, was named "The World's Best Cruise Line" for the second year in a row by Tour and Travel News based on the votes of its travel agent readers.  Royal Caribbean ships currently include the new <I>Legend of the Seas</I> and <I>Splendour of the Seas</I>, with four ships on order to be delivered within the next 2 years.<p>

Royal Caribbean Cruises has been in business for 25 years, and is the winner of prestigious industry awards year after year.<p>

For additional information on this special travel value, contact your local <a href="aaaoffices.html">AAA/CAA club office</a>.<p>
