<H3>Members Only Vacation Values:</H3>
Take advantage of the exciting travel opportunities and discounts that come with your AAA membership.<p>

As a member, when you book your Seabourn cruise vacation through a AAA Travel Agency, you are eligible to receive special "SHARE" savings on select sailings ranging from $500 to $2,500 per person.<p>

<H3>About Seabourn Cruises:</H3>
<img align="left" width=200 height=134 src="seabournephoto2.gif" alt="seabournephoto2.gif">

Seabourn offers the ultimate luxury cruise experience for the affluent, discriminating leisure traveler who expects only the best on his or her vacation.  Seabourn ships offer the personalized service and exclusivity of a yacht combined with the full array of services and amenities available on a deluxe large liner.  Emphasis is placed on providing the highest level of personal service available on a cruise.  The staff and crew are graciously at each guest's beck and call.<p>

For additional information on this special travel value, contact your local <a href="aaaoffices.html">AAA/CAA club office</a>.<p>
