<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Tauck Tours</TITLE></HEAD><BODY LINK="#0000bf" VLINK="#ee0000" BGCOLOR="#ffffff" BACKGROUND="aaatile.gif"><center><table cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0><TR><TD><a href="seabourncruises.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="prev.gif" alt="PREV"></a></TD><TD><a href="welcome.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="home.gif" alt="HOME"></a></TD><TD><a href="index.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="navigate.gif" alt="Navigate"></a></TD><TD><a href="trafalgartours.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="next.gif" alt="NEXT"></a></TD></TR>
</table><h1>Tauck Tours</h1></center>
<H3>Members Only Vacation Values:</H3>
<img align="right" width=250 height=167 src="taucktoursphoto1.gif" alt="taucktoursphoto1.gif">

Take advantage of the exciting travel opportunities and discounts that come with your AAA membership.  When you book your Tauck Tour vacation through a AAA Travel Agency, you can take advantage of outstanding travel offers available only to AAA members.  See your local AAA Travel Agency for more details.<p>

<H3>About Tauck Tours:</H3>
<img align="left" width=200 height=133 src="taucktoursphoto2.gif" alt="taucktoursphoto2.gif">

Tauck is a three-generation, family-owned tour company that consistently wins top travel honors.  In both 1994 and 1995, Tauck was voted the prestigious World Travel Award as the "Top North America Tour Company," and Tauck also won the American Society of Travel Agents (ASTA) award for the past seven years as the "#1 Tour Company in America."  Since 1925, Tauck Tours has achieved a loyal client following like no other tour operator in the world.  Fully 98% of Tauck travelers say they plan to travel with the company again.<p>

Featuring deluxe escorted vacations to Alaska, Canada, USA, Europe, China, Southeast Asia, Australia and New Zealand, Hawaii, Costa Rica and Belize, and Mexico, Tauck Tours are in a class by themselves.<p>

For additional information on this special travel value, contact your local <a href="aaaoffices.html">AAA/CAA club office</a>.<p>

