<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Trafalgar Tours</TITLE></HEAD><BODY LINK="#0000bf" VLINK="#ee0000" BGCOLOR="#ffffff" BACKGROUND="aaatile.gif"><center><table cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0><TR><TD><a href="taucktours.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="prev.gif" alt="PREV"></a></TD><TD><a href="welcome.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="home.gif" alt="HOME"></a></TD><TD><a href="index.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="navigate.gif" alt="Navigate"></a></TD><TD><a href="travelimpressions.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="next.gif" alt="NEXT"></a></TD></TR>
</table><h1>Trafalgar Tours</h1></center>
<H3>Members Only Vacation Values:</H3>
<img align="left" width=122 height=326 src="trafalgarphoto1.gif" alt="trafalgarphoto1.gif">

Trafalgar Tours, the world's No. 1 vacation choice to Europe, features land-only packages and a choice of exceptionally priced air-inclusive packages from all major U.S. gateways with a choice of airlines, for memorable and hassle-free vacations.<p>

As a AAA member, you are entitled to an exclusive AAA member benefit when you book a Trafalgar Tour. Choose Trafalgar's comprehensive Travel Insurance at a cost of just $25 per person (regularly $79 - $99 per person), or choose a $25 voucher per person toward payment of selected optional tours on escorted motorcoach packages.<p>

You can use your member benefit on Trafalgar Tours packages year round.  Take a Trafalgar "Winter Break" this year, packages with land-only prices as low as $33 per person per day -- and a special member benefit!<p>

Other savings opportunities* include:
<UL>
<LI>Savings for children:  25% for 5-12 years;  10% for 13-17 years and for three sharing a room.
<LI>"Friendly Five" discount for five people traveling together.
<LI>Second tour discount on First Class and Cost Saver tour packages (when booking back-to-back tours).

</UL>
<br clear=all>
*  Not available on "Winter Break" packages.

<H3>About Trafalgar Tours:</H3>
<img align="right" width=133 height=200 src="trafalgarphoto2.gif" alt="trafalgarphoto2.gif">

Trafalgar Tours has specialized in First Class European escorted tours since 1947 and boasts a customer satisfaction rate of 97%.  Today, vacation options include independent and escorted tours to Europe and Britain with year-round departure dates on many itineraries.  Trafalgar became #1 to Europe by offering top quality and value, including:

<UL>
<LI>Superior Hotels
<UL>
<LI>First Class hotels in 91 cities throughout Europe including daily breakfast.
</UL>
<LI>Heathrow & Gatwick Hospitality Desks
<UL>
<LI>Airport information/reception desks at London Heathrow and Gatwick airports with meet and greet transfers.
<LI>Free transfers at other European Gateways.
</UL>
<LI>Tour Directors/Local Guides
<UL>
<LI>"Best in the Business."  All Tour Directors are experienced, professional and multi-lingual with a minimum of 5 years travel experience.
</UL>
<LI>Luxury air-conditioned or jet ventilated motorcoaches depending on destination 
<LI>Mix of English-speaking nationalities on board.
<LI>Savings on extra hotel nights in London and other popular European cities.
<LI>Convenient Currency Paks available for sale on many Trafalgar Tours.
<LI>And much more.
</UL>

For additional information on this special travel value, contact your local <a href="aaaoffices.html">AAA/CAA club office</a>.<p>

