<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Travel Impressions</TITLE></HEAD><BODY LINK="#0000bf" VLINK="#ee0000" BGCOLOR="#ffffff" BACKGROUND="aaatile.gif"><center><table cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0><TR><TD><a href="trafalgartours.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="prev.gif" alt="PREV"></a></TD><TD><a href="welcome.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="home.gif" alt="HOME"></a></TD><TD><a href="index.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="navigate.gif" alt="Navigate"></a></TD><TD><a href="windstarcruises.html"><img align="middle" border=0 width=100 height=40 src="next.gif" alt="NEXT"></a></TD></TR>
</table><h1>Travel Impressions</h1></center>
<H3>Members Only Vacation Values:</H3>
<img align="right" width=200 height=61 src="travelimpressionlogo.gif" alt="travelimpressionlogo.gif">

Take advantage of the exciting travel opportunities and discounts that come with your AAA membership. When you book your Travel Impressions vacation through a AAA Travel Agency, you will receive a $25 food/beverage credit at selected hotels at each destination.<p>

<H3>About Travel Impressions:</H3>
<img align="left" width=200 height=136 src="travelimpphoto2.gif" alt="travelimpphoto2.gif">

Travel Impressions brings you the romance and excitement of the Caribbean, Mexico and Florida.  Imagine yourself in a climate where the sunshine is endless, the warmth is invigorating and there is always a refreshing cool breeze; where beaches are sugar white and baby powder soft, and the temperate seas are a perfect aquamarine blue.<p>

Specializing in the Caribbean, Bahamas, Bermuda, Mexico and Florida, Travel Impressions offers any day departures from gateways nationwide.  Travel Impressions offers budget to deluxe vacation packages to fit anyone's taste and budget.  For families, singles, couples and honeymooners, travel to all the popular sun destinations.  As a long-established, customer-driven business, we personally oversee every aspect of your vacation.<p>

As a family owned and operated business with over 2 million travelers served since 1974, Travel Impressions takes great pride in its reputation as one of the most experienced and service-oriented tour operators.<p>

For additional information on this special travel value, contact your local <a href="aaaoffices.html">AAA/CAA club office</a>.<p>

